kpi_info.title: RRC SETUP FAIL DUE TO AC CODE
kpi_info.use: The number of RRC setup failures caused by Admission Control because of downlink spreading code congestion. M1001C3 is also updated along with this counter. UPDATED: When the RNC decides to reject the RRC connection request because of downlink spreading code congestion.
